Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:05.54,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}君が見る夢は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.58,0:01:09.33,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}古いインクで紙に書いた祈りのよう　
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.38,0:01:12.88,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}小さなその手が縋るものも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.92,0:01:16.13,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}今はまだ何処にも無い
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.22,0:01:18.59,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}それでも君の行く道を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.68,0:01:21.68,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}綺麗なものは綺麗なままで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.81,0:01:25.56,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}守り続けたいと思うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.40,0:01:34.11,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}空と水が星を染めて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.36,0:01:40.41,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}淡く虹を描いて散って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.45,0:01:46.58,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}眩しい夜君が歌う
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.66,0:01:53.17,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}声は何処まで届くのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.38,0:02:01.09,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}憧れの住まう 蒼い星のひかり
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.18,0:02:05.77,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}ただ僕らは恋をして
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.85,0:02:11.65,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}たった一つの未来の為に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.69,0:02:18.20,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}今の全て奏でてみる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.28,0:02:19.91,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}飛び立つよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.07,0:02:24.66,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}まだ暗い空へ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:05.54,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}你心中的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.58,0:01:09.33,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}就如以古老的墨水写下的祈祷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.38,0:01:12.88,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}那双稚嫩的双手的追求
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.92,0:01:16.13,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}至今仍未见得一缕希望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.22,0:01:18.59,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}但为了你选择的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.68,0:01:21.68,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}永远纯粹永不褪变
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.81,0:01:25.56,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}我依然会一直地守护
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.40,0:01:34.11,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}天空和海水给这个星球上色
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.36,0:01:40.41,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}描绘出淡淡的虹彩又慢慢消散
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.45,0:01:46.58,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}闪耀的夜里 你高声歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.66,0:01:53.17,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}这些歌声究竟能传至何处
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.38,0:02:01.09,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}寄托着憧憬的蓝色星球的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.18,0:02:05.77,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}我们是如此的眷恋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.85,0:02:11.65,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}为了仅仅的一个未来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.69,0:02:18.20,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}奏响现在拥有的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.28,0:02:19.91,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}我们会再次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.07,0:02:24.66,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}翱翔于那片黑暗的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.20,0:20:53.14,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}０ 起始也好 终结也好 那是改变的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.84,0:21:03.66,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}不再低下视线 不再举手遮挡 ALD
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.72,0:21:10.81,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}noah 那时候总是罗列不合尺码的谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.28,0:21:19.66,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}迷茫自失 是自己 造成了所有的失败
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.16,0:21:26.48,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}AS 照耀 影与荣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.54,0:21:35.34,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}反复地计算 明日零时的信号
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.65,0:21:45.90,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}看不见的光芒轨迹 只见文字 离开赖以生存的杀戮场
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.06,0:21:54.11,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}那个连名字也没有的地方 又何从寻求答案
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.13,0:22:03.47,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}生命的雨丝 融入风中 汹涌而出的泪水 不言放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.57,0:22:13.85,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}期待黑暗终结全都不要 只要回归零点 回归裸足的phrase-1
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.20,0:20:53.14,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}０ 始まりにも 終わりにも 変わる光
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.84,0:21:03.66,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}下に向けたまま かざすのを止めた あの時 ALD
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.72,0:21:10.81,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}noah サイズの合わない 嘘ばかり並べて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.28,0:21:19.66,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}見失い 自ら全てに つまずいた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.16,0:21:26.48,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}AS 照らす 影と栄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.54,0:21:35.34,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}繰り返すcount 明日の零時のサイン
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.03,0:21:37.61,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}LIVE or DIE
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.65,0:21:45.90,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}見えない 光の線 文字だけで 生kill-場所捨てて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.06,0:21:54.11,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}名前も居ない そこに 答えを求めてても
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.13,0:22:03.47,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}風にとかした 命のRain 投げ捨てない 駆け出しのナミダ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.57,0:22:13.85,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}期待も闇も終りもいらない ゼロになれば 裸足のphrase-1
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.91,0:02:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32\pos(640,424)}令正义伸张 哪怕天堂坠落
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.89,0:00:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 托利尔兰男爵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.28,0:00:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的扬陆城即将进入地球捕食
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.03,0:00:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激光通信马上也要切断
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.19,0:00:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就长话短说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.72,0:00:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灭鼠行动的状况如何了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.11,0:00:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.46,0:00:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不行 你还需要静养
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.46,0:00:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.60,0:00:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是学校
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.92,0:00:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人还没有注意到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.44,0:00:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们算是暂时逃出生天了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.10,0:00:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.58,0:00:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说伊奈帆他们吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.67,0:00:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们说要去战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.40,0:00:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用这里的装备
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.92,0:00:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那架火星重甲骑兵战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(OP)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.54,0:02:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 这到底是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.63,0:02:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是总部的指令
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.49,0:02:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要市民的避难一结束
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.68,0:02:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就放弃这个基地 全员撤离
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.82,0:02:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有同伴在战场上战斗啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活下来的只有你一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.05,0:02:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鞠户孝一郎上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.50,0:02:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.95,0:02:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达尔扎娜·马格巴丽吉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.95,0:02:53.43,ruby,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Darzana Magbaredge
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.70,0:02:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四护卫舰队所属 强袭登陆舰海神号的舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.13,0:03:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是不见咲薰副长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.41,0:03:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北区还有战友留在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.16,0:03:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里之所以没事是因为她在那里拖着敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.55,0:03:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.68,0:03:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,界冢雪准尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.08,0:03:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电波干扰覆盖了整个新芦原区域
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.66,0:03:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GPS也不好用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.50,0:03:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算现在赶过去救援 也无法得到她的位置情报
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.48,0:03:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.40,0:03:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的任务是护送载有难民的渡船
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.82,0:03:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有来不及跑的平民
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.54,0:03:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘客目录上也没有那些小孩的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.96,0:03:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是我的学生！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.14,0:03:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 我会向司令部申请组成救援队
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.73,0:03:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会留下一艘登陆艇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.12,0:03:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果无法凑够驾驶登陆艇的人数
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.42,0:03:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候…你就放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.40,0:03:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿奈 你在里面吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.53,0:03:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.57,0:03:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.58,0:03:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啊 所以才来找你的！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.82,0:04:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道自己正准备干什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.28,0:04:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常清楚这很疯狂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.51,0:04:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.96,0:04:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个火星人 不知道为何一心想来干掉我们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.78,0:04:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.72,0:04:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我们在这里拖住他的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.58,0:04:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的攻击便不会波及到市区及海港
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.57,0:04:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所幸的是这一带的市民避难都完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.42,0:04:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.97,0:04:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起助死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.19,0:04:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“要学会随机应变”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.23,0:04:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“如果有什么万一的话 要相信自己做出决断”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.35,0:04:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪姐 你一直有和我说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.39,0:04:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得现在正是那个时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.96,0:04:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.50,0:04:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能交给伤员
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.48,0:04:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.57,0:04:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很不安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.18,0:04:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我希望雪姐去保护他们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.76,0:05:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓励那些害怕的人 让他们安心下来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.57,0:05:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是我们做不到的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.38,0:05:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下 明明你是一位比任何人都渴望和平的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.72,0:05:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是谁…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.56,0:05:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说 你不仅仅没有杀掉老鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.69,0:05:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还失去了他们的踪迹？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.24,0:05:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恕我直言 扎赫巴姆大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.64,0:05:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我托利尔兰还没有让他们逃脱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.10,0:05:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.13,0:05:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们逃入隧道后所能移动的范围是有限的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.23,0:05:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 他们就在这个新芦原北区
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.69,0:05:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当他们不耐烦从地下露头的刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.29,0:05:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这Nilokeras引以为豪的鹰眼会马上…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.43,0:05:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.25,0:05:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得我们有时间和他们耗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.45,0:05:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算找不到老鼠的确切位置也无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.16,0:05:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要将整个城市给炸毁就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.97,0:06:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将进行陨石爆击
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.12,0:06:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎…扎赫巴姆大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.45,0:06:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 这里离库鲁迪欧伯爵的扬陆城太近了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.38,0:06:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这会被当成对他的攻击吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.89,0:06:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些时候 牺牲是必要的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.96,0:06:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轨道修正需要几个小时的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.21,0:06:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你密切监视老鼠们 确保他们没有在此期间跑到其他地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.12,0:06:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.85,0:06:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.21,0:06:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我整理的关于那架火星重甲骑兵的资料
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.22,0:06:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙不是将雪姐打出的枪弹反弹 而是全部吸进去 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.95,0:06:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电波状态如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.31,0:06:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勉勉强强
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.85,0:06:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耍小聪明！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.40,0:06:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.33,0:06:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅仅是枪弹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.88,0:07:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有源传感器的信号传递到它的身上也不会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.88,0:07:01.39,ruby,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(359,655)}active sensor
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.25,0:07:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.97,0:07:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红外 声波探测以及雷达都不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.85,0:07:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有回波返回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.20,0:07:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅仅是运动能量 电波和激光也会被吸收
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.22,0:07:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为这一定是那堵墙的特性
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.79,0:07:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墙？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.72,0:07:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指覆盖那家伙表面的能量护壁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.41,0:07:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以叫做防护壁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.43,0:07:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防护壁…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.89,0:07:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.03,0:07:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物体 光 声音 电波
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.41,0:07:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能吸收任何接触到它的物质的护壁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.92,0:07:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这样的话 那家伙是如何看到护壁外侧的情况的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.59,0:07:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.61,0:07:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面的情报全部都被防护壁给遮断了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.03,0:07:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许那家伙无法透过防护壁看到和听到这边的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H576368&\3c&HFBFDFD&\fn@WenQuanYi Micro Hei\frz298.8\pos(768,133)}吸收
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H576368&\3c&HFBFDFD&\fn@WenQuanYi Micro Hei\frz286.6\pos(918,306)}防护壁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H576368&\3c&HFBFDFD&\fn@WenQuanYi Micro Hei\frz272.9\pos(956,652)}吸收
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.23,0:08:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我看来 这护壁的内侧应该是漆黑一片的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.67,0:08:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那家伙的攻击为什么会打中我们呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.85,0:08:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 如果看不到的话 要如何瞄准呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.49,0:07:57.33,bar,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H5D666E&\3c&HF9FCFC&\pos(1052,151)}光
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.45,0:07:57.33,bar,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H5D666E&\3c&HF9FCFC&\pos(1098,275)}声
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.37,0:07:57.33,bar,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1159,412)}电 波
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.86,0:08:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙从大楼的另一侧准确地攻击了逃跑中的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.15,0:08:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 之前明明紧追着我们不放
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.55,0:08:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我们进入隧道的时候 就很干脆地放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.97,0:08:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到护壁外面的一定不是他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.16,0:08:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得那家伙为了确保视野 一定在天空上布置了其他摄像机
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.41,0:08:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.25,0:08:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不管和他拉开多远的距离 他都能追上我们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.57,0:08:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但却不愿意进入隧道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.91,0:08:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为开着护壁没办法看到前面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.82,0:08:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙现在应该也在天上监视着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.20,0:09:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.04,0:09:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反过来说 只要我们就这样在屋檐下不动 就会很安全呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.49,0:09:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我们出去的瞬间就会被发现
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.46,0:09:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机会大概只有一次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.15,0:09:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,备用电池已经没有了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.21,0:09:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这周是谁负责检查的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.61,0:09:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的鞠戸…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.21,0:09:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说伊奈帆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.22,0:09:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶重甲骑兵出击的是我们三个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.74,0:09:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我们还需要两人来开卡车去充当诱饵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.86,0:09:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.84,0:09:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让我…来帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.26,0:09:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.28,0:09:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北欧美女
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.96,0:09:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得我有责任去承担这个危机 这个试炼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.34,0:09:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中二病？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.69,0:09:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.11,0:09:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙杀了我的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.52,0:09:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也让我来帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.71,0:10:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这边也是拼了命的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.78,0:10:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.58,0:10:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.99,0:10:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明早行动 日出之时出发
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.39,0:10:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们来击退那架火星重甲骑兵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(PartB)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.19,0:10:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在工作吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.17,0:10:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,韵子你呢 不去睡吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.50,0:10:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会议室太冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.47,0:10:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟把空调给关掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.93,0:10:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望尽可能地减少这里有人居住的迹象
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.89,0:10:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡姆睡得可死了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.58,0:10:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望他别感冒了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.19,0:10:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.59,0:10:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这时候了你还担心别人感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.42,0:10:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天我们可能就会死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.23,0:10:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.61,0:10:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.58,0:11:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.07,0:11:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是那么大无畏的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.14,0:11:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原以为能救到他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.75,0:11:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是却被那么轻易地…简单地…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.66,0:11:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算那一刻到来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.55,0:11:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定连做觉悟的时间都没有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.49,0:11:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那一刻会怎样地去后悔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.66,0:11:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无法忍受静静地待着去想那些事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.08,0:11:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是我还是卡姆 我觉得都是如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.01,0:11:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果韵子不想来的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.06,0:11:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.35,0:11:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了明天 我去睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.03,0:11:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奈帆 别感冒了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.35,0:11:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.46,0:11:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次感谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.52,0:12:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们5个人接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.24,0:12:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将开始执行营救新芦原北区的遗留友军以及难民的作战行动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.34,0:12:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请追加一人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.70,0:12:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马格巴丽吉舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.12,0:12:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡轮的护卫交给不见咲副长全权负责了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.31,0:12:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边作战结束以后应该会来和我们汇合的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.03,0:12:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓紧时间出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.88,0:12:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对你有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.46,0:12:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鞠户孝一郎上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.89,0:12:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看那个！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.07,0:12:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信号弹…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.55,0:12:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三发红色的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.75,0:12:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是学校那边！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.63,0:12:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然开始战斗了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.11,0:13:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小老鼠…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.83,0:13:10.50,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,May I have seen your face somewhere sometime?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.79,0:13:12.17,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You freeze my blood and spine
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.22,0:13:13.71,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So freak me out
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.88,0:13:15.88,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like a look in a mirror
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.05,0:13:17.98,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Face my Doppelgäger
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.14,0:13:21.02,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How 'bout you? Aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.41,0:13:26.24,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Beware of attentions, entourages and mates
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.43,0:13:29.80,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You are what you do
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.54,0:13:34.24,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Depress your metions, ain't got to be a bighead
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.36,0:13:37.66,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You are what you fool
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.84,0:13:38.61,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right now
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.69,0:13:40.54,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Burn your soul, neck or nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.68,0:13:43.74,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Burn it out 'til you're losing your reason
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.96,0:13:46.44,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Forget the stoned reason to drive it
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.64,0:13:48.54,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just to scribe your existence
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.68,0:13:50.44,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not a crime, your insistence
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.62,0:13:53.66,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Die another day
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.86,0:13:54.60,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So do I
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.71,0:13:56.50,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Burn my soul, all to nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.62,0:13:59.85,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Burn it out, let me charge in your advance
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.00,0:14:02.49,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm watching for the chance to beat it
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.60,0:14:04.54,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even though my body's shaking
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.66,0:14:06.44,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give it all, deadly bumping
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.65,0:14:09.50,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cuz you make me feel
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.55,0:14:11.05,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Breathless
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.78,0:14:26.58,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right now
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.68,0:14:28.52,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Burn your soul, neck or nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.61,0:14:31.69,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Burn it out 'til you're losing your reason
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.86,0:14:34.46,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Forget the stoned reason to drive it
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.57,0:14:36.45,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just to scribe your existence
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.63,0:14:38.42,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not a crime, your insistence
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.58,0:14:41.76,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Die another day
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.93,0:14:42.59,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So do I
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.69,0:14:44.49,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Burn my soul, all to nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.64,0:14:47.80,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Burn it out, let me charge in your advance
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.94,0:14:50.52,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm watching for the chance to beat it
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.69,0:14:52.46,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even though my body's shaking
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.67,0:14:54.48,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give it all, deadly bumping
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.69,0:14:57.53,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cuz you make me feel
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.70,0:14:59.08,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Breathless
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.92,0:15:14.59,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right now
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.66,0:15:16.44,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Burn your soul, neck or nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.60,0:15:19.66,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Burn it out 'til you're losing your reason
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.89,0:15:22.40,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Forget the stoned reason to drive it
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.58,0:15:24.46,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just to scribe your existence
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.63,0:15:26.39,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not a crime, your insistence
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.59,0:15:29.30,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Die another day
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.86,0:15:30.48,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So do I
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.59,0:15:32.51,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Burn my soul, all to nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.61,0:15:35.84,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Burn it out, let me charge in your advance
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.02,0:15:38.56,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm watching for the chance to beat it
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.68,0:15:40.45,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even though my body's shaking
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.62,0:15:42.48,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give it all, deadly bumping
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.63,0:15:45.43,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cuz you make me feel
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.65,0:15:46.83,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Breathless
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.14,0:13:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就来收拾你们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.82,0:13:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发了 请跟上我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.92,0:13:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 路太窄了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.47,0:13:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心 今天是不会扣分的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.25,0:13:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了 10点方向
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.61,0:13:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现了呢 西瓜虫！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.56,0:13:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战开始！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.15,0:13:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.56,0:14:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙的动作停下了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.16,0:14:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奈帆说得没错！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.69,0:14:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.88,0:14:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开保险 举起它 发射
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.82,0:14:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很简单吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.48,0:14:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这群可恶的老鼠！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.22,0:14:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧 界冢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.66,0:14:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鞠戸上尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.71,0:14:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托利尔兰男爵！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.28,0:14:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.94,0:14:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我可没听说会有这东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.46,0:14:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拖车呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.74,0:14:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.37,0:14:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我位置 他们在哪！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.91,0:14:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西…西南方向 好像正往城市的中心部前进
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.96,0:15:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙太乱来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.91,0:15:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掩护我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.94,0:15:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架蝙蝠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.31,0:15:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙的气流把烟雾都吹散了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.62,0:15:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须将它打下来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.07,0:15:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 卡姆！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.98,0:15:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球的重甲骑兵…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.39,0:15:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.77,0:15:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡姆！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.66,0:15:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.89,0:15:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.17,0:15:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 安定装置虽然被打中了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.17,0:15:36.61,ruby,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(551,655)}stabilizer
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.69,0:15:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但还是能勉强跑起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.64,0:15:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙能被炮弹打中的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.62,0:15:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sky Carrier
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.38,0:15:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴斯的战术运输机
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.50,0:15:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说除了机枪和导弹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.20,0:15:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就没有其他任何特殊装备或者特殊能力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.68,0:16:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烟幕！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.76,0:16:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.46,0:16:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电压检测
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.82,0:16:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,油压检测
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.12,0:16:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温度检测
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.55,0:16:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回转数正常
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.70,0:16:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力反馈检测程序开始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.70,0:16:16.39,ruby,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Force feedback checking program start
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.84,0:16:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弹射座椅正常
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.84,0:16:19.19,ruby,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(603,655)}Ejection seat
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.75,0:16:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,IFF确认
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.51,0:16:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战术数据链 激活
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.26,0:16:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.82,0:16:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全系统正常
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.82,0:16:26.95,ruby,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,System all green
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.47,0:16:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开启固定装置
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.47,0:16:28.37,ruby,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hold Open
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.46,0:16:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想跑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.55,0:16:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离目的地还有1200米 离汇合预定时间还有93秒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.80,0:16:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来争取时间 稍微安静点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.18,0:17:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我当傻子耍吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.10,0:17:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浪费我精力…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.51,0:17:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑 他的目标是我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.44,0:17:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 离汇合预定时间还有54秒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.50,0:17:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.24,0:17:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真丢人啊…都这个时候了还来求饶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.15,0:17:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退下！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.65,0:17:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以巴斯第一皇女之名 绝不会容忍这种暴行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.57,0:18:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟拉姆·巴斯·艾莉欧西亚公主殿下！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.91,0:18:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.13,0:18:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退下！无礼之人！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.71,0:18:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能…怎么可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.20,0:18:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全弹发射 目标敌人火星重甲骑兵！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.84,0:18:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.50,0:18:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.61,0:18:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主臂开关 射击控制 放下减震器后…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.54,0:18:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,韵子 快点！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.46,0:18:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 真是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.32,0:18:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的 Nilokeras可是拥有铁壁般的防御
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.33,0:18:40.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你这种渣…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.65,0:18:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,误差修正 0-1-6 0-1-2！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.35,0:18:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.35,0:18:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射！发射！发射！发射！发射！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.88,0:19:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.44,0:19:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.36,0:19:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡姆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.51,0:19:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.27,0:19:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脚底？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.70,0:19:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.71,0:19:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.07,0:19:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.12,0:19:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水没有被吸进去的地方！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.44,0:19:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背面装甲 进气阀右下 爪子的缝隙中！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.53,0:19:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.36,0:19:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你的护壁有缝隙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.02,0:19:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说地面的接触面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.66,0:19:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脚掌上是无法展开护壁的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.83,0:19:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你这样做的话 你站都站不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.92,0:19:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的护壁正因为很无敌所以才没办法包裹全身
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.67,0:19:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外部摄像机的数据接收部也是护壁缝隙之一
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.34,0:20:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我朋友的那份
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.92,0:20:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.46,0:20:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.40,0:20:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.76,0:20:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是火星的公主…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.05,0:20:46.05,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“战场上的孩子们”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(ED)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.92,0:22:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托利尔兰男爵 您平安无事！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.36,0:22:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是来挖苦我的吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.15,0:22:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才你都去哪了！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.67,0:22:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为Sky Carrier做应急处理去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.31,0:22:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我带路！赶紧离开这个地方！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.06,0:22:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下！亚瑟拉姆殿下还活着！这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.75,0:22:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.45,0:22:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以下一次一定要确保把她给杀死！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.11,0:22:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要蠢到什么地步啊 劣等人种！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.78,0:22:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果让她活着 我们一族就会背上反贼的罪名啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.16,0:22:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.96,0:23:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙 你打算做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.61,0:23:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿来！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.90,0:23:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那场游行 图谋暗杀公主殿下的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.42,0:23:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会…后悔的…
